# Normalize line endings: store text files with LF in the repo and check them
# out with LF on every platform. Fixes the mixed CRLF/LF state where a handful
# of files (e.g. some .tsx/.ts/.py) were committed with CRLF and produced noisy
# `git diff --check` trailing-whitespace warnings and whole-file EOL diffs.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary types: never touch EOL (git auto-detects these too, but be explicit).
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.svg text eol=lf
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
